{"thag1.60:0.1":"Theragatha 1.60 ","thag1.60:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.60:0.3":"Chatthavagga ","thag1.60:0.4":"Sivalittheragatha ","thag1.60:1.1":"“Te me ijjhimsu sankappa, ","thag1.60:1.2":"yadattho pavisim kutim; ","thag1.60:1.3":"Vijjavimuttim paccesam, ","thag1.60:1.4":"mananusayamujjahan”ti. ","thag1.60:1.5":"… Sivalitthero … ","thag1.60:1.6":"vaggo chattho. ","thag1.60:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag1.60:2.1":"Godhiko ca subahu ca, ","thag1.60:2.2":"valliyo uttiyo isi; ","thag1.60:2.3":"Anjanavaniyo thero, ","thag1.60:2.4":"duve kutiviharino; ","thag1.60:2.5":"Ramaniyakutiko ca, ","thag1.60:2.6":"kosalavhayasivaliti. "}